      <title>两个邮箱配置两个SSH</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/13/%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E9%82%AE%E7%AE%B1%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AASSH/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/13/%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E9%82%AE%E7%AE%B1%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AASSH/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一般来说,一台电脑上配置两个SSH密钥是很正常的嘛，两个邮箱对应两个SSH.<br>假设原来在C盘中/Users/xxx/.ssh目录下已经生成了一个密钥对：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">id_rsa.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成第二个key<br>接下来我们生成第二个ssh key：</p><p>ssh-keygen -t rsa -c “<a href="mailto:yourmail@gmail.com">yourmail@gmail.com</a>“<br>这里不要一路回车，我们自己手动填写保存路径：</p><p>Generating public/private rsa key pair.<br>Enter file in which to save the key (/c/Users/xxx/.ssh/id_rsa): /c/Users/xxx/.ssh/id_rsa_github<br>再按回车三次<br>这时我们返回电脑的C盘/Users/xxx/下id_rsa_github来区别原id_rsa。<br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tivenny/pic/master/uklwigSl3n.png" alt="图1"></p><p>完成之后，我们可以看到~/.ssh目录下多了两个文件，变成：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">id_rsa</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">id_ras.pub</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">id_rsa_github</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">id_rsa_github.pub</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">known_hosts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后到[github](<a href="https://github.com/）" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/）</a> 上登陆自己的github帐号，点击右上角图像向下箭头，找到setting,进入找到ssh and GPG keys,如下两图所示，把C盘/Users/xxx/里的github_rsa.pub以记事本的方式打开，把里面的代码copy到下图的红框框中。</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tivenny/pic/master/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720200412182803.png" alt="图2"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tivenny/pic/master/InkedQQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20200412182432_LI.jpg" alt="图3"><br>ok! 完事</p>]]></content>
      
      
